comments: Hart (POR) is the last to touch the ball before it goes out of bounds.
Simons (POR) briefly rests his arm on Booker's (PHX) hip.
Simons (POR) establishes himself in Ayton?s (PHX) path and some contact occurs during the screen attempt.
Nurkic (POR) is set in Bridges' (PHX) path and marginal contact occurs during the pick.
Ayton (PHX) makes contact with the ball before the ball touches the backboard.
Simons (POR) brings his arm toward Booker?s (PHX) path and marginal contact occurs at the start of Booker?s (PHX) drive.
Hart (POR) jumps up vertically and absorbs the contact initiated by Booker (PHX) during Booker's driving shot attempt.
Nurkic (POR) makes incidental contact with Booker (PHX) after the release of Booker's shot attempt.
Nurkic (POR) is set in Bridges' (PHX) path and some contact occurs during the pick.
Grant (POR) contacts the ball after it has made contact with the backboard and it still has an opportunity to score.
Simons (POR) is set in Ayton's (PHX) path and maintains a legal screening position as Ayton goes over the top of the screen.
Nurkic (POR) slightly extends his arms into Bridges' (PHX) as Nurkic is rolling toward the rim.
Replay review of the defensive goaltending called on Ayton (PHX) is overturned. Ayton makes contact with the ball before it has reached its apex.
Paul (PHX) reaches across Nurkic's (POR) body and delivers contact to Nurkic's arm at the start of his upward shooting motion.
Nurkic (POR) jumps from A to B and delivers body contact to Bridges (PHX) during his driving shot attempt.
Ayton (PHX) cleanly deflects Lillard's (POR) pass.
Booker (PHX) extends his leg during the jump shot attempt but avoids making contact with Lillard (POR).
Paul (PHX) moves towards Grant (POR) as he secures the rebound and the contact is marginal.
Paul (PHX) stops short of initiating contact with Lillard (POR), who begins his shooting motion with his right leg extended to the side and the contact is marginal.
Lee (PHX) makes incidental hand-on-ball contact with Hart (POR) during his driving shot attempt.
Ayton (PHX) is set in Lillard's (POR) path and some contact occurs during the pick.
Lee (PHX) delivers body contact to Nurkic (POR) during his shot attempt.
Ayton (PHX) delivers contact to Grant (POR) as he attempts to set the screen.
Ayton (PHX) is in a legal guarding position when incidental contact occurs with Grant (POR) during his dunk attempt.
Ayton (PHX) is set in Grant's (POR) path and maintains a legal screening position during the screen.
Bridges (PHX) makes incidental contact with Hart's (POR) arm as both players reach for the rebound.
Booker (PHX) cleanly dislodges the ball from Lillard (POR) during the rebound attempt. Any ensuing contact is incidental.
Lee (PHX) gets beat to the spot and delivers body contact to Lillard (POR) during his shot attempt.
Hart (POR) is moving alongside Booker?s (PHX) path and marginal body contact occurs as they come together at the end of the drive.
Paul (PHX) and Hart (POR) make incidental contact with each other during the inbound.
Bridges (PHX) moves alongside Simons? (POR) path and marginal body contact occurs during Simons' drive.
Booker (PHX) briefly holds Lillard (POR) as he is moving on the perimeter but does not affect his FOM.
Nurkic (POR) and Lee (PHX) mutually engage and disengage as Lee is running on the perimeter.
Hart (POR) moves alongside Booker?s (PHX) path and some contact occurs at the end of the drive.
Ayton (PHX) is set in Hart's (POR) path and does not deliver contact during the screen.
Replay review of the foul called on Nurkic (POR) pursuant to a coach?s challenge was deemed unsuccessful. Nurkic makes contact to Ayton's (PHX) arm that affects his shot attempt at the rim.
Nurkic (POR) and Landell (PHX) mutually engage and disengage as both players are boxing out on the free throw line.
Landale (PHX) places an arm against Nurkic's (POR) back and marginal contact occurs as he releases to reach for the long rebound.
